50|$|Open Cargo or Shipper’s Interest Insurance: This {{policy may}} be {{purchased}} by a carrier, <b>freight</b> <b>broker,</b> or shipper, as {{coverage for the}} shipper’s goods. In the event of loss or damage, this type of insurance {{will pay for the}} true value of the shipment, rather than only the legal amount that the carrier is liable for.|$|E
