5000|$|The <b>freight</b> <b>broker</b> bond {{increase}} {{took effect}} on October 1, 2013. Many freight brokers were against this change because they expected they wouldn't {{be able to}} meet the new requirement: it was a 7-fold increase, moreover the previous price was set constant for about 40 years.According to FMCSA there had been too many cases where shippers and carriers had been delayed (or entirely denied) payment so the bond increase was necessary.|$|E
